      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Actor Jehan Appuhamy, who was wanted for defying court order, was released on bail by the Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage, after being surrendered to the court today.",
        "He was released on two sureties of Rs.500,000 each by the magistrate."
